title: Matrix Multiplication
description: Given two matrices, calculate their product. The first line contains four integers: R1, C1, R2, C2, representing the dimensions of the two matrices. It is guaranteed that C1 = R2. The following R1 lines contain C1 integers each for the first matrix. The next R2 lines contain C2 integers each for the second matrix.
input_format: The first line contains R1, C1, R2, C2. Then R1 rows of matrix 1, followed by R2 rows of matrix 2.
output_format: R1 rows containing C2 integers each, representing the product matrix.
